# Data Structures

## Category (object)
+ name: `Category` (required, string)
+ slug: `cat1` (required, string)
+ description: `This is the category description` (string)

## Categories Relationship (object)
+ id: 1 (string)
+ type: categories (string)

## Category Relationships Base (object)
+ include Project Categories Relationship

## Category Response (object)
+ data
  + id: `1` (string)
  + type: `categories` (string)
  + attributes(Category, required)
  + relationships(Category Relationships Base, required)

## Categories Response (object)
+ categories
  + data(array[Category], required)

## Comment (object)
+ markdown: `Markdown` (string)
+ body: `Body` (string)
+ state: `published` (enum[string])
  + Default `published`
  + Members
    + `published`
    + `edited`
+ edited_at: `2014-07-07T18:01:26.000Z` (string)
+ created_at: `2014-07-07T18:01:26.000Z` (string)

## Comment Base (object)
+ markdown: `Markdown` (string, required)

## Head For Comment (object)
+ id: `1` (string, required)
+ type: `comments` (string, required)

## Head For Comment Create (object)
+ type: `comments`, (string, required)

## Attributes For Comment (object)
+ attributes: (Comment, required)

## Attributes For Comment Create Or Update (object)
+ attributes: (Comment Base, required)

## Relationships For Comment (object)
+ relationships:
  + include Related Posts
  + include Related Users
  + include Related Comment User Mentions

## Relationships For Comment Create (object)
+ relationships: (Related Posts, required)

## Comment Create Request (object)
+ include Head For Comment Create
+ include Attributes For Comment Create Or Update
+ include Relationships For Comment Create

## Comment Update Request (object)
+ include Head For Comment
+ include Attributes For Comment Create Or Update

## Comment Response (object)
+ include Head For Comment
+ include Attributes For Comment
+ include Relationships For Comment

## Comments Response (object)
+ comments
  + data(array[Comment Response], required)
+ included(array[Comment User Mention Response])

## Related Comments (object)
+ comments
  + data(array[Head For Comment])

## Comment User Mention (object)
+ indices : 'Debug'
